==English==
===Noun===

'''citadel'''

# A strong [[fortress]] that sits high above a [[city]].
# A stronghold or [[fortified]] place.

===Etymology===

[[w:French|French]] citadelle, from [[w:Italian|Italian]] cittadella, diminutive of città, city, from [[w:Latin|Latin]] cīvitās.


